      "heading": "Physical network interface EdgeRouter X SFP consists of 5 Gigabit Ethernet ports, as well as one slot for SFP-module.",
      "text": "Physical network interface EdgeRouter X SFP consists of 5 Gigabit Ethernet ports, as well as one slot for SFP-module. This allows the router to be integrated into any network structure, including fiber optic. It is important to note that this model supports Passive PoE 24V - it allows you to power up to 5 connected clients. At the same time, the router itself can be powered from 220V through the 24VDC connector using the included adapter."
